-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-24/cheung-kong-sells-350-flats-at-new-project-sing-tao-reports.html
Cheung Kong Holdings Ltd. (1)  sold 350
flats at its La Splendeur residential project yesterday, Sing
Tao Daily reported, citing the developer.  Prices for the project located in Tseung Kwan O range from
about HK$5,000 to HK$6,000 per square foot, the paper said,
citing the companyâ€™s Executive Director Justin Chiu.  A Shanghai buyer surnamed Liu spent a total of HK$50
million buying seven flats for investment, the newspaper
reported. The buyer is investing in  Hong Kong  because of
property purchase limits in mainland China, the paper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
